5. Constraints and Limitations  
 All modifications have been made within the original HTML file. No external libraries or assets have been added.  
 The new rotation mechanic replaces the swap mechanism; any further advanced animations or UI indicators (such as dedicated row/column selectors) can be implemented later but are not required at this stage.  

